>探しています。</span>\n    </h1>\n</section>\n<section class=\"recruit js_waypoint\" data-waypoint_offset=\"70%\">\n    <div class=\"inner\">\n        <p class=\"recruit_txt\">\n            経験者の⽅はもちろん、<br>\n            新卒の⽅、業界業種が未経験の⽅、<br>\n            Iターン・Uターン就職、転職のみなさん、<br>\n            九州で、宮崎で、都城市で働きませんか？<br>\n            当社の理念に共感し、<br>\n            私たちと⼀緒に働いてくれる仲間を募集します。\n        </p>\n        <ul class=\"recruit_list\">\n            <li class=\"js_waypoint\">\n                <div class=\"recruit_item_cover\">\n                    <img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"recruit_item_x\" src=\"/img/home/recruit_1.png\" width=\"314\" height=\"384\" alt>\n                </div>\n            </li>\n            <li class=\"js_waypoint\">\n                <div class=\"recruit_item_cover\">\n                    <img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"recruit_item_x\" src=\"/img/home/recruit_2.png\" width=\"314\" height=\"384\" alt>\n                </div>\n            </li>\n            <li class=\"js_waypoint\">\n                <div class=\"recruit_item_fukidashi_wrap\">\n                    <div class=\"recruit_item_fukidashi\">\n                        <p class=\"recruit_item_fukidashi_txt\">\n                            <b>Iターン・Uターン</b><br>\n                            積極採用！\n                        </p>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"recruit_item_cover\">\n                    <img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"recruit_item_x\" src=\"/img/home/recruit_3.png\" width=\"315\" height=\"384\" alt>\n                </div>\n            </li>\n            <li class=\"js_waypoint\">\n                <div class=\"recruit_item_cover\">\n                    <img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"recruit_item_x\" src=\"/img/home/recruit_4.png\" width=\"314\" height=\"384\" alt>\n                </div>\n            </li>\n        </ul>\n    </div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"requirement_contact\">\n    <div class=\"entry_bnr_wrap inner\">\n        <div class=\"entry_bnr animate_fadeup_str js_waypoint\">\n            <p class=\"entry_bnr_ttl\">\n                <span class=\"entry_bnr_ttl_en\">New graduate</span>\n                <span class=\"entry_bnr_ttl_jp\">新卒の方はこちら </span>\n            </p>\n            <a href=\"/newgraduate/\" class=\"entry_bnr_btn js_link\">\n                <span class=\"entry_bnr_btn_txt\">募集要項を見る</span>\n                <span class=\"entry_bnr_btn_icon\"></span>\n            </a>\n            <a href=\"/entry/\" class=\"entry_bnr_btn entry_bnr_btn_entry js_link\">\n                <span class=\"entry_bnr_btn_txt\">エントリーする</span>\n                <span class=\"entry_bnr_btn_icon\"></span>\n            </a>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"entry_bnr animate_fadeup_str js_waypoint\">\n            <p class=\"entry_bnr_ttl\">\n                <span class=\"entry_bnr_ttl_en\">Mid-career</span>\n                <span class=\"entry_bnr_ttl_jp\">中途の方はこちら </span>\n            </p>\n            <a href=\"/midcareer/\" class=\"entry_bnr_btn js_link\">\n                <span class=\"entry_bnr_btn_txt\">募集要項を見る</span>\n                <span class=\"entry_bnr_btn_icon\"></span>\n            </a>\n            <a href=\"/entry/\" class=\"entry_bnr_btn entry_bnr_btn_entry js_link\">\n                <span class=\"entry_bnr_btn_txt\">エントリーする</span>\n                <span class=\"entry_bnr_btn_icon\"></span>\n            </a>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"inner\">\n        <div class=\"requirement_contact_inner js_waypoint animate_fadeup_str\">\n            <h2 class=\"requirement_contact_ttl fw900\">まずは話を聞いてみたい方</h2>\n            <p class=\"requirement_contact_txt\">\n                エントリー前に、会社説明や会社見学、<br class=\"sp_only\">インターンをご希望の方は、<br class=\"pc_only\">下記いずれかの方法にてお気軽にご連絡ください。\n            </p>\n            <ul class=\"requirement_contact_list\">\n                <li>\n                    <h3 class=\"requirement_con